  <brief_title>Cardiac Effects in Long-Term Survivors of Hodgkin's and Non-Hodgkin's Lymphoma</brief_title>
  <official_title>Cardiac Effects in Long-Term Survivors of Hodgkin's and Non-Hodgkin's Lymphoma After Radiation Therapy/Anthracycline Chemotherapy</official_title>
