  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is to inquire by mailed survey regarding the cardiac and general health of
      patients previously treated for Hodgkin's and non-Hodgkin's lymphoma with radiation
      therapy/anthracycline chemotherapy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
