  <eligibility>
    <study_pop>
      <textblock>
        Patients previously treated at the University of Rochester Department of Radiation
        Oncology.
      </textblock>
    </study_pop>
    <sampling_method>Non-Probability Sample</sampling_method>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  All patients with Hodgkin's Lymphoma and Non Hodgkin's lymphoma who underwent
             Radiation Therapy (RT) to either a mantle or modified mantle field with or without
             adriamycin at the Wilmot Cancer Center at the University of Rochester are eligible for
             the study.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Any severe preexisting cardiac disease (e.g., arrhythmia, angina, coronary disease,
             myocardial infarction, or congestive heart failure) prior to diagnosis
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
